(X,\Omega,\mu)
f
X
 \mu\left(\{x\in X : |f(x)|\geq t\}\right)\leq \frac{1}{t}\int_X |f|~d\mu  
\{x\in X : |f(x)|\geq t\}
A
A=\{x\in X : |f(x)|\geq t\}
\chi_A(x)=\mathbf 1(x\in A)
 \mu\left(\{x\in X : |f(x)|\geq t\}\right)=\int_{A} ~d\mu =\int_{X} \chi_A ~d\mu  
 \mu\left(\{x\in X : |f(x)|\geq t\}\right)=\int_{X} \chi_A  ~d\mu \\ = \int_{X} \frac{t}{t}\chi_A ~d\mu  \leq \int_{X} \frac{|f|}{t}\chi_A ~d\mu  \\ \leq \int_{X} \frac{|f|}{t}~d\mu  \\ 
 \mu\left(\{x\in X : |f(x)|\geq t\}\right)=\int_{X} \chi_A  ~d\mu \\ = \int_{X} \frac{t^2}{t^2}\chi_A ~d\mu \leq \int_{X} \frac{f^2}{t^2}\chi_A ~d\mu  \\ \leq \int_{X} \frac{f^2}{t^2}~d\mu  \\ 
